BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF OHIO:
Section 1. That section 3301.25 of the Revised Code be 4
enacted to read as follows: 5
Sec. 3301.25. (A) The department of education and 6
workforce shall establish the community connectors workforce 7
program to support connecting students to jobs, internships, and 8
career professionals in their communities. 9
(B)(1) The department shall oversee the program, and each 10
educational service center shall administer the program for the 11
school districts it serves. Each educational service center 12
shall, to the extent that funds are appropriated by the general 13
assembly to do so, employ at least one, but not more than three, 14
individuals to work as directors in high schools in the 15
districts to which it provides services. Each educational 16
service center shall determine the number of directors it 17

